                                <li><i class="fa fa-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Automatically route leads to your team. </li>
                                <li><i class="fa fa-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> A Full 2-way email sync with Gmail and Office 365. </li>
